'''Akarere k’Evren''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Evren ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere k’Evren ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 4.513 (abagabo 2.253 n’abagore 2.260)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 179,74 .

